I was so excited about going on a cruise here. I was so shocked regarding the amount of people to be fair, there‚Äôs busy and then there is chaos! This was chaos around the area where you embarked and disembarked. Keep sight on the people that you are with as you can easily loose sight of them. It is definitely worth doing at least once. I would not want to do it again as once you have seen it you have seen it. It is a fabulous sight to see and to wake up on the water in kind of magical. I wished we had chosen a better boat and paid a little more. Saw some magnificent hawks whilst there too, which was my highlight! I would not go again, like other places I have visited due to the massive amount of people there at the same time. But if you have not seen it you really should.
